{"tid":1604513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以應承我 唔好再叫啲狗做阿SIR","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:52:53.000Z","uid":74213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d03210ffddf045f8bb1ee277f1fd6e729dbb2baa","tid":1604513,"uid":74213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"可能你地覺我都係一句<br />\n但係阿SIR 係一個尊稱<br />\n阿SIR 嘅用法係:<br />\nused as a formal and polite way of speaking to a man, especially one who you are providing a service to or who is in a position of authority:<br />\nWould you like to see the menu, sir?<br />\n&quot;Did you hear what I said?&quot; &quot;Yes, Sir.&quot;<br />\n見到手足比人打緊仲阿SIR 前阿SIR 後做乜鳩<br />\n以後全部人一係叫啲狗做毅進仔、一係叫黑警再唔係叫返警察<br />\n你叫佢阿SIR 佢地會不自覺覺得自己高高再上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3d423171f8e9df70697bcd1f736a8ba9413ab8","tid":1604513,"uid":302905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"雖然冇咩壞，但我覺得套制服同gear先令佢地自覺高高在上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫咩都唔當你同我係人架啦，中意叫咩大家自便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76548d351fa838718e4c4ada271c57d9801060ff","tid":1604513,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"認同"}]}